Author: PhattSticc
Text: I know. Like the amount I ate doesn't also make me feel like a blimp as well, lol. I'm hoping one day I eat like a normal person, maybe one day I could loose weight normally. I hope you get rid of that little voice, it's horrible. The guilt is really bad and it's hard to get past that.

Author: Peanut2ur_Tostito
Text: I know this is easier said than done, but please try not to worry about it. You ate more because you had restricted so much for a while. That's ok! I do the same when I restrict. One day isn't going to make you gain weight. I usually have about one day a week where I allow myself to eat like a normal person. I'm doing it slowly, but surely. One day I hope to eat normally & not hear that awful voice in my head beating me up for it.
